{"tid":348813,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚7點［英雄聯盟王者邀請賽決賽］ 中国 vs 台港隊","createTime":"2017-08-06T05:03:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T07:17:44.000Z","uid":2997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d33c36333e2b40909be192c4125440f0a8eabc66","tid":348813,"uid":2997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:03:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/06/125849_78df727e093d3f1da84b879ade2cd397.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F06%2F125849_78df727e093d3f1da84b879ade2cd397.jpg&h=6c63305a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中国隊陣容：若風(Misaya) 、微笑(WeiXiao) 、草莓(CaoMei) 、卷毛(Fzzf) 、Ruo <br />\n<br />\n台港tpa陣容：MiSTakE、Stanley、Liballz、GodJJ、Toyz <br />\n<br />\n　　由香港旅遊發展局主辦的香港電競音樂節特別舉辦《英雄聯盟》王者回歸世界邀請賽，邀請過去《英雄聯盟》知名選手進行表演賽。首局今日上午由台港澳隊對上歐洲隊，雖然台港澳隊率先取下一分，但歐洲隊馬上又扳回一局，最終台港澳隊以 2：1 擊敗歐洲，晉級 8 月 6 日晚間 7 時舉辦的決賽。<br />\n<br />\n直播網址<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.twitch.tv/esl_lol\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.twitch.tv%2Fesl_lol&d=RXwih5i%2FRi3UFcgrGh8mwZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=a08c487a\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.twitch.tv/esl_lol</a><br />\n<br />\n正啊，屌 台港澳入左決賽打支那隊啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n岩岩買左飛去現場支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf41b134e0060597dc698349c7925374cadae8f8","tid":348813,"uid":2997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:13:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c8d431e2618f3f7ec329a5141e6100ec64537a7","tid":348813,"uid":121324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited